snippet.textDisplay:
A pure magical song.. Everything I hear I fall in love more deeply with this song.. After publishing this song everyday after the office I hear this song repeatedly at home which gives me very much relaxation.. The singers, especially Shiblu bhai, what melodious tunes he got! It's like a lot of honey loaded in his voice, so much soothing, then Mam Aleya Begum she has such a gracious voice! It’s like her voice explaining so much love, pain, so many stories even novels, pure raw feelings and also the sound of soil, the other chorus has done a tremendous job, the girls singing like opera and the group with Mam Aleya Begum are just awesome.. Now, if I have to talk about Emon bhai, what a great musician he is!? He just lives on those instruments.. He is a very talented musician. That first tune with the leaf that made me so amazed and astonished.. This is a real talent.! Mithun Chakra and the other musicians made extraordinary, soulful vibes which made the song one of the greatest songs of the word..
Thank you so much Coke Studio Bangla.. 🇧🇩❤💗 Thank you all singers and musicians, you all made us so much proud, you all are pride of Bangladesh 🇧🇩💗 Thank you for bringing our Bangladeshi songs and cultures so beautifully.. Keep it up.. 
Joy Bangladesh 🇧🇩💗
